    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a smooth, worry-free experience on the road. It\u2019s clean, well-loved, and ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so you can just hop in and go. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re really going to love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
