    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit exhibits excellent compression across all cylinders and a recently serviced double VANOS system for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to address known chassis fatigue, and the cooling system features an upgraded aluminum radiator to prevent thermal expansion issues. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, offering a direct connection to the tarmac. It rides on staggered Style 67 alloys with high-performance compound tires. This is an expertly maintained example optimized for the purist driver.",
